name: Elephant Tee
description:
This elephant tee was designed by Nicole Bailey one our of student artists here at Campus Apparel. Contact us if you are interested in getting in touch with her for a custom design or piece of artwork.

The high quality print is based on a hand drawn image for extra precision printing. The tee itself is a crew neck custom fit t-shirt for extra comfort and style, made from 100% cotton.
